The Pickled People
Gherkin Off

Gherkin Off by The Pickled People is what it is.  Nothing fancy, nothing particularly thought out.  Quickly assembled.  Written and recorded at the same time.  Using simple tools at my disposal.  Humble everything, not an attempt at fame.  Just a challenge. 

Volumes 1-3 are pulled from 60 demos written in a 2 week span at the start of 2013.  There will be more volumes to follow.
